		 Wednesday, May 05, 2004 				 																				Jyoti Basu								Former chief minister, government of West Bengal, and CPM politburo member																																							It is obvious that common people will be benefitted if elections are held only on Saturdays and Sundays. But the poll schedule is drawn up by the Election Commision officials in Delhi and they have to keep the national perspective and prerogatives in mind. So there is nothing that we can do about it here.
